(1) outerWidth
---------------
==> returns the outer width of the browser window, including all interface elements (like toolbars/scrollbars).


EX
-------

	window.outerWidth  // Get Window Outer Width
	
	Or
	
	outerWidth   // Get Window Outer Width
	
	
(2) outerHeight
---------------
==> returns the outer height of the browser window, including all interface elements (like toolbars/scrollbars).


EX
-------

	window.outerHeight  // Get Window Outer Height
	
	Or
	
	outerHeight   // Get Window Outer Height
	
